      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "pn50 hypervisor:\n  resolvectl → ~ocp.rhuk.local → 192.168.127.1 (virbr-ag)\n  NM dispatcher script for persistence\n\nbastion VM:\n  NM dnsmasq plugin → server=/ocp.rhuk.local/192.168.127.1\n\nairgap dnsmasq (192.168.127.1):\n  Host records: bastion, api, api-int, bootstrap, master-0/1/2\n  Wildcard: *.apps.ocp.rhuk.local → 192.168.127.5",
