      "updated": 1710700000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API (control plane):\n  api.ocp.rhuk.local:6443 → bastion HAProxy → masters:6443\n\nMachine Config:\n  api-int:22623 → bastion HAProxy → masters:22623\n\nIngress:\n  *.apps.ocp.rhuk.local → bastion HAProxy → masters\n\nImage pulls (disconnected):\n  masters → bastion:8443 (mirror-registry via airgap)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API (control plane):\n  api.ocp.rhuk.local:6443 → bastion HAProxy → masters:6443\n\nMachine Config:\n  api-int:22623 → bastion HAProxy → masters:22623\n\nIngress:\n  *.apps.ocp.rhuk.local → bastion HAProxy → masters\n\nImage pulls (disconnected):\n  masters → bastion:8443 (mirror-registry via airgap)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
